td-54dec5: Account HMAC Keys
Status: [open]
Type: epic | Priority: P2
Labels: account-hmac-keys

Description:
Each account needs a unique per-tenant HMAC key so audit chain integrity remains cryptographically isolated. This change adds storage, generation, and retrieval of 32-byte account HMAC keys for GA.Audit.Chain.

Artifacts:
- Proposal: openspec/changes/account-hmac-keys/proposal.md
- Design: openspec/changes/account-hmac-keys/design.md
- Tasks: openspec/changes/account-hmac-keys/tasks.md
- Specs: openspec/changes/account-hmac-keys/specs/key-management/spec.md

